Another. It is powerful to cure irritation in the bladder by giving it with water of honey. It is also powerful for those who are not able to urinate when it is given as a drink with a decoction of garlic.

Another. It is powerful in toothache. Put 8 drops with as much garlic juice and put it warm on the tooth that hurts.

Another. It is powerful in cough. Give it with a wine decoction of mallow or of hyssop and of nettle seed.

